    "Besides, foundational text analysis functions like text retrieval and frequency count have also been further enhanced in the Evol platform.",
    "Its interface supports both Chinese and English, catering to the needs of users worldwide, without requiring a programming background.",
    "Hierarchical text reuse for intertextual analysis.",
    "When creating literary works, humans deliberately or inadvertently reuse texts from others, resulting in innate intertextual networks within the literature.",
    "These intertextual networks provide traceable evidence for the dissemination and evolutionary trajectory of human ideas."
